.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBeodinga index --root ~/projects --root ~/docs\fR
Build or refresh the index for multiple roots.
.TP
\fBeodinga search 'date:this-week ext:md roadmap' --limit 20\fR
Run a CLI search using the shared query DSL.
.TP
\fBeodinga stats --json\fR
Print the active index snapshot and in-memory counters as JSON.
.TP
\fBeodinga doctor\fR
Check dependencies, writable paths, roots, and hotkey support.
